flowRoot.flowPara: 5th Leg is the (type)face of openSUSE. A geometric sans serif to be used as a headline font in all openSUSE materials. I would like to make this a default font for the window decorations in the defualt theme for 11.2, Sonar.
v0.3 has improved metrics, but still nowhere near being good enough.
